^B@2^*BHoward: ^*N|cp||at|Vulnerability is a factor, but only on very close decisions. Do not over worry about vulnerability, especially at IMPs, where you rarely get doubled in partials. Okay, a couple of other things to consider as well, but less important than the total number of trumps. |
